# Project 04 — IndiGo Airlines Business Health Analysis ✈️

## Overview
Analysis of 50,000 IndiGo Airlines booking records to evaluate business 
health across revenue, customer behaviour, and booking patterns.

## Tools Used
- MySQL — data querying and analysis
- Excel — data cleaning, pivot tables, and dashboard

## Dataset
50,000 customer booking records including seat class, booking channel, 
add-ons, flight day, and booking completion status.

## Key Findings
1. Only 14.88% of bookings are completed — 85.12% are abandoned
2. Business class generates 41.88% of total revenue
3. 88.6% of bookings come via Internet — Mobile is underutilised at 11.2%
4. Weekend flyers pay 17% more than weekday flyers
5. Customers with all 3 add-ons generate 150% more revenue
## Files
- indigo_clean.csv — cleaned dataset
- Indigo_Airlines_Analysis.xlsx — Excel workbook with dashboard
